<doc id="747283" wikidata="Q112967643" url="?curid=747283" title="U.S. Route 32">
<text>U.S. Route 32 (US 32) was a U.S. Highway from 1926 to 1934, which ran along present-day:
*U.S. Route 6 from Omaha, Nebraska to Princeton, Illinois
*U.S. Route 34 from Princeton, Illinois to Chicago, Illinois

